targets.query:
from(bucket: "delfi_pq")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "RadioEPSTelemetry")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "PanelYpCurrent" or r["_field"] == "PanelYmCurrent" or r["_field"] == "PanelXpCurrent" or r["_field"] == "PanelXmCurrent")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["status"] == "Valid")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: "delfi_pq")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "RadioEPSTelemetry")

  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["status"] == "Valid")
  |> group(columns:["_field"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
